Instructions to generate the pdf version of the user manual
on Linux Debian or Ubuntu or equivalent distributions.
-----------------------------------------------------------

1. You need open office and unoconv packages installed.

2. Change directory to AVC doc directory.

3. Run converter.
   cmd: odt2pdf user_manual.odt
